lead_paragraph: Scrumhalf Maxime Machenaud will start France’s Six Nations game against Wales in Cardiff on Friday as manager Guy Noves made five changes to his team on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Machenaud at Scrumhalf as France Make Changes for Wales
